body_html:
Passed docker-trigger https://ci.pytorch.org/jenkins/job/caffe2-docker-trigger/99/ (with retries https://ci.pytorch.org/jenkins/job/caffe2-docker/job/py2-centos7/87/ and https://ci.pytorch.org/jenkins/job/caffe2-docker/job/py2-cuda8.0-cudnn7-centos7/80/ and https://ci.pytorch.org/jenkins/job/caffe2-docker/job/py3.5-clang3.9-ubuntu16.04/54/ and https://ci.pytorch.org/jenkins/job/caffe2-docker/job/conda3-cuda8.0-cudnn7-ubuntu16.04/51/).

Passed master https://ci.pytorch.org/jenkins/job/caffe2-master/977/ , except for current failing builds. Don't think those builds should be affected by these conda-only changes anyways.
